folder: Castleton Avenue & Davis Avenue, Staten Island, NY
text:
(1) Castleton Ave., at the N.E. corner of Davis Ave., showing St. Marys Protestant Episcopal Church.

May 7, 1926.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The Davis Ave. side of the church.

May 1, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.

(3) Another view of the Davis Ave. side of the church. On the left is the parsonage.

May 1, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.
